2011-01-10|2011-01-16.description: These Draculas just don’t know when to quit! Deadpool's already shown them they’re no match for his kill-skills, yet they continue to step to him. Are they just suckers for punishment, or are they setting him up? Silly draculas…tricks are for Deadpool!
2011-01-10|2011-01-16.name: I Rule, You Suck Part 2

2011-01-10|2011-01-16.description: The Atom and the Justice League guest-star as Ray Palmer comes to some dark conclusions regarding Ryan Choi's murder. Meanwhile, the Tattooed Man must finally decide what kind of man he is when Deathstroke hands him his son's killer, while Osiris has already chosen his path in bringing back his sister Isis – but what will Osiris do when he runs into Shazam?
2011-01-10|2011-01-16.name: Family Reunions, Part 4: The Fate We Make

2011-01-31|2011-02-06.description:
It’s the ultimate battle between friend and family as Spidey’s battle against the Iron Patriot and his Dark Avengers leaves one man with a choice too painful to contemplate.

Plus, as Peter Parker prepares for the second most important wedding day of his life, a new enemy brutally rises up from Spidey’s past. Plus the introduction of some brand new family members promises to make this a wedding that he wishes never happened!

Includes material reprinted from Amazing Spider-Man #599 and Amazing Spider-Man Annual #36! 76 pages! £2.95

2011-02-07|2011-02-13.description: This new perfectbound collection contains two full issues worth of classic strips from Knights of the Dinner Table #99 to the double-sized #100, crammed between two sturdy covers! It's always a great time to pick up these hysterically funny strips, so don't miss out on this incredible addition to any gamer's shelf!
2011-02-07|2011-02-13.name: Volume Thirty-One

volume.name: Knights of the Dinner Table: Bundle of Trouble

2011-02-28|2011-03-06.description:
Part 1 of the 3-part "The Darkest House," the story readers have been demanding. A member of the Secret Six attempts to bring back a fallen loved one by using the demonic "Get Out of Hell Free" card stolen back in the first arc of the series! And as it turns out, Hell wants the card back...

After having a nightmare of Knockout being trapped in Hell, Scandal Savage discovers that Ragdoll has taken the teams Get out of Hell Free Card. After a brief fight between Savage and Ragdoll, in which the rest of the team watches, Ragdoll reveals that he wants to use the card to save Parademon. After Ragdoll escapes to Hell the team votes to fallow him, all except Black Alice who is only willing to show them to the Gates of Hell.

Once on the elevator to Hell the team is greeted by The Demon, who informs them that they have been sold out by Ragdoll who now has an army at his control.

Meanwhile, Liana is kidnapped by a man who is planning on torquing her and deprogram her of her wicked ways.
2011-02-28|2011-03-06.name: The Darkest House, Part One of Three: In Every Dream a Nightmare

2011-03-21|2011-03-27.description: Red Hulk is already used to his past sins coming back to haunt him. Now, even the good he's done has created a deadly new challenge. The world stage bursts open to make room for a powerful mastermind who wants to remake society in her own vision--after she kills the Red Hulk! Plus: a mysterious group has plans for their newly adopted champion--Rick Jones, the A-Bomb!
2011-03-21|2011-03-27.name: The Next Life; Save the Date, Part Two

  • Aus dem Leben eines Taugenichts

  • Die gemopste Formel
  • Kraft ist nicht alles

2011-05-09|2011-05-15.description:
A Ship to Cross a Sea of Suffering

Someone is hunting down Elephantmen, one by one... Hip Flask is on the killer's trail.
2011-05-09|2011-05-15.name: Man & Elephantman Part 2 of 3: A Ship To Cross A Sea Of Gathering

2011-06-27|2011-07-03.description: Translates Bruce Wayne: The Road Home: Batman and Robin, Bruce Wayne: The Road Home: Red Robin, Bruce Wayne: The Road Home: Batgirl, Bruce Wayne: The Road Home: Outsiders, Bruce Wayne: The Road Home: Catwoman and Bruce Wayne: The Road Home: Commissioner Gordon.
Translates Peter Parker #1-2 and The Amazing Spider-Man #634-637.

2011-08-01|2011-08-07.description: Translates The Brave and the Bold #19-22.

2011-08-15|2011-08-21.description: “Inside Job” Part Three: Scourge the Hedgehog, evil doppelganger to Sonic, is half-way to his goal: put together a gang and bust out of Zone Jail! But first he’ll need to win the loyalty of two of the most dangerous members of the Destructix. If he can survive that, the rest is easy: fighting an army of Zone Cops and rival inmates!
2011-08-15|2011-08-21.name: Inside Job, Part Three

2011-09-12|2011-09-18.description: HorrorHound delves into the world of science-fiction horror with a special issue dedicated to The Thing from Another World and other body-snatching creatures from space. We dissect the greatest sci-fi space monsters of all time, from The Deadly Spawn and H.R. Giger's Aliens to the unstoppable bugs of Starship Troopers - all in celebration of the impending The Thing prequel. Comic book and movie news as well as Video Invasion, Horror's Hallowed Grounds and Collect This! are all included.

2011-09-19|2011-09-25.description:
10-year-old Negi Springfield has just graduated from a British school for wizards. After meeting with the school headmaster to discuss his graduate work assignment, he finds that he will be moving to Japan--to teach English at an all-girls high school. Under strict instructions not to show his magic powers, Negi finds that he can't resist using them to help others. Of course, despite his good intentions sometimes his magic just makes things even worse!

Chapter Titles

  • 277th Period: Annihilation of the Magical World!!?
  • 278th Period: Outcome! Battle At the Peak of the Magical World!!
  • 279th Period: The Negi Party -- The World's Only Hope!!
  • 280th Period: The Maidens Strike Back!!
  • 281st Period: Negi Party, Hard Aport!! Full Speed Ahead!!
  • 282nd Period: Find the Key to Victory!!
  • 283rd Period: Fierce Attack On Asuna ♥
  • 284th Period: The Captive Imperial Princess
  • 285th Period: Prescription For Darkness
2011-09-19|2011-09-25.name: Magical Annihilation

2011-09-26|2011-10-02.description:
FEAR ITSELF TIE-IN

Hel ain't a bad place to be...unless it's been overrun by forgotten horrors and ancient gods, clamoring to swallow all creation. Then it kinda sucks. While the events of Fear Itself tear the world apart, Dani Moonstar has followed the calling of her Valkyrie blood to the Viking underworld to save the queen of the dead. Can the rest of the New Mutants make it to Hel in time to save her and the souls of Valhalla from total Oblivion?
2011-09-26|2011-10-02.name: Fear Itself Tie-In Part 3

2011-10-03|2011-10-09.description: Heath Huston fights the secret rulers of the universe in the wake of the null bang. It begins with the countdown to the finale. Also, a special Tales of the Fear Agent by legendary creator Hilary Barta.
2011-10-03|2011-10-09.name: Out Of Step, Part 4

2011-10-31|2011-11-06.description: As Earth remains in the grip of terror, and society’s heroes desperately try to defend its people, the Plutonian’s rage has been driven to heights by revelations about his past. After sacrifice, hope, and death, is it truly too late to stop the Plutonian? This arc-ending issue will leave IRREDEEMABLE fans reeling! Find out what everyone is talking about in the latest installment of Mark Waid’s multiple Eisner and Harvey Award-nominated superhero series!

2011-11-07|2011-11-13.description: The game-changing, twice-monthly epic called "Tommy Taylor and the War of Words" begins now! Tom Taylor goes to war against the cabal that has tormented, imprisoned and tried to destroy him – and it's far more than just a war of words! To have a hope of winning, Tom must use every weapon he can get hold of, but even storybook magic carries its own risks. And for a story unlike any you've ever seen, one issue a month isn't enough! In the special, standalone .5 issues, Tom's crusade plays out against the backdrop of the cabal's sinister secret history and delves deep into the dark past of some of the series' major players. When it's all over, very little will remain Unwritten.
2011-11-07|2011-11-13.name: Part One of Tommy Taylor and the War of Words

2011-12-05|2011-12-11.description: CHAOS is over. The future holds many mysteries, but the past can never be forgotten. As Ironhide looks back at what was, he comes to realize that it may hold the key to what lies ahead. A new peace has settled, and a new time has come for the Autobots, for the Decepticons... for Cybertron.
2011-12-05|2011-12-11.name: Pax Cybertronia
